title: Open Tabs # 36
itunes:title: Open Tabs # 36
description:
Welcome to Open Tabs! The show where I leave all of the tabs open on my browser and go through them with you! 

Today, I sit down with my cousin Andrew and my producer Halston. We watch Da Baby’s bowling alley fight, his music videos, Freddie Gibbs freestyle, Pearl Jam vs Mötley Crüe, and more! 

 

For video submissions you can email Halston@bertbertbert.com 

 

For all TOUR DATE & MERCH click HERE: http://www.bertbertbert.com
